title: Indonesia: Repeal abhorrent bylaw that imposes flogging for consensual sex (Amnesty International Australia)
text: ( Source : Amnesty International Australia ) Authorities in the Indonesian region of Aceh must immediately repeal a controversial new bylaw which imposes harsh flogging sentences for consensual sex in some instances and could make it easier
